<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-29-0813 </DOCNO><TEXT>A compact CsI(Tl)/photodiode gamma-ray detector is described which iscapable of locating the point of interaction of incident gamma-ray photonsin the spectral region around 1 MeV. Laboratory tests are used to quantifyboth the spectral and positional resolutions of the detectors. Theirlikely application in space gamma-ray astronomy is also discussed.</TEXT></DOC>